{
  "video_id": "wF3nhile788",
  "title": "This could change Facebook forever",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 200.0,
      "end_time": 3130.0,
      "text": "- Last year, we found out that for the past three years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3130.0,
      "end_time": 5180.0,
      "text": "Facebook had been deleting the messages"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 5180.0,
      "end_time": 7479.0,
      "text": "of Mark Zuckerberg and some other executives"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 7480.0,
      "end_time": 9600.0,
      "text": "and in the controversy that followed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 9600.0,
      "end_time": 11260.0,
      "text": "the company promised that it would then"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 11260.0,
      "end_time": 14100.0,
      "text": "allow all of us to do exactly the same thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 14100.0,
      "end_time": 15469.0,
      "text": "Imagine my surprise this week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 15470.0,
      "end_time": 17700.0,
      "text": "when Mark Zuckerberg announced that he was going"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 17700.0,
      "end_time": 19900.0,
      "text": "to lean hard into privacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 19900.0,
      "end_time": 20910.0,
      "text": "It's a lot of talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 20910.0,
      "end_time": 24260.0,
      "text": "It was 3,200 words in a blog post that Zuckerberg wrote."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 24260.0,
      "end_time": 25660.0,
      "text": "To understand what it all means,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 25660.0,
      "end_time": 28100.0,
      "text": "we're going to have to look at the big picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 31240.0,
      "end_time": 33900.0,
      "text": "So what did Mark Zuckerberg actually say in his blog post?"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 33900.0,
      "end_time": 37140.0,
      "text": "He said he wanted to bring end to end encryption"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 37140.0,
      "end_time": 39400.0,
      "text": "to all of Facebook's messaging products."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 39400.0,
      "end_time": 40750.0,
      "text": "That means Facebook Messenger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 40750.0,
      "end_time": 42410.0,
      "text": "WhatsApp and Instagram Direct."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 42410.0,
      "end_time": 44400.0,
      "text": "One of the things that he says in his blog post"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 44400.0,
      "end_time": 46670.0,
      "text": "is that encryption limits services like ours"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 46670.0,
      "end_time": 48470.0,
      "text": "from seeing the content flowing through them"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 48470.0,
      "end_time": 50300.0,
      "text": "and makes it much harder for anyone else"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 50300.0,
      "end_time": 51790.0,
      "text": "to access your information."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 51790.0,
      "end_time": 54440.0,
      "text": "And once your messages are end to end encrypted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 54440.0,
      "end_time": 57730.0,
      "text": "that means that no one from Facebook or the government"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 57730.0,
      "end_time": 60370.0,
      "text": "will ever be able to understand the contents"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 60370.0,
      "end_time": 61309.0,
      "text": "of your messages."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 61310.0,
      "end_time": 63630.0,
      "text": "The second major thing that was in the blog post"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 63630.0,
      "end_time": 65850.0,
      "text": "was the idea that your messages"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 65850.0,
      "end_time": 67390.0,
      "text": "should no longer be permanent."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 67390.0,
      "end_time": 69340.0,
      "text": "Zuckerberg speculated that in the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 69340.0,
      "end_time": 72230.0,
      "text": "your messages on Facebook would disappear by default,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 72230.0,
      "end_time": 74600.0,
      "text": "after a certain period of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 74600.0,
      "end_time": 76320.0,
      "text": "You could choose to keep them if you wanted to"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 76320.0,
      "end_time": 77679.0,
      "text": "but just like on Snapchat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 77680.0,
      "end_time": 79410.0,
      "text": "how messages disappear when you read them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 79410.0,
      "end_time": 81980.0,
      "text": "if you wanted your Facebook to feel like that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 81990.0,
      "end_time": 83000.0,
      "text": "all of a sudden, it could."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 83000.0,
      "end_time": 84910.0,
      "text": "So with those two ideas out there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 84910.0,
      "end_time": 87780.0,
      "text": "Facebook says it is going to rally around privacy"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 87780.0,
      "end_time": 89570.0,
      "text": "in a way that it never has before."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 89570.0,
      "end_time": 92130.0,
      "text": "If you've read a story about Facebook in the past year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 92130.0,
      "end_time": 95390.0,
      "text": "chances are it was about a privacy scandal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 95400.0,
      "end_time": 97500.0,
      "text": "whether it was Cambridge Analytica last spring"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 97500.0,
      "end_time": 100470.0,
      "text": "or the biggest data breach in company history last fall."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 100470.0,
      "end_time": 102690.0,
      "text": "So when Zuckerberg says that privacy is now"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 102690.0,
      "end_time": 104899.0,
      "text": "the most important thing to Facebook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 104900.0,
      "end_time": 105970.0,
      "text": "a lot of people are skeptical."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 105970.0,
      "end_time": 107920.0,
      "text": "But let's say that you believe Zuckerberg,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 107920.0,
      "end_time": 110470.0,
      "text": "what would that mean for Facebook and the rest of us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 110470.0,
      "end_time": 112100.0,
      "text": "Well, one of the things that he says is"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 112100.0,
      "end_time": 113610.0,
      "text": "in the future, we're going to want"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 113610.0,
      "end_time": 115935.0,
      "text": "the world to feel less like a town square"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 115935.0,
      "end_time": 118200.0,
      "text": "and more like a living room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 118200.0,
      "end_time": 121790.0,
      "text": "so less yelling in pubic, more talking to your friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 121790.0,
      "end_time": 123510.0,
      "text": "If that's true, it has a lot of"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 123510.0,
      "end_time": 125190.0,
      "text": "big implications for Facebook."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 125190.0,
      "end_time": 128900.0,
      "text": "Number one, the news feed is no longer the most"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 128900.0,
      "end_time": 129519.0,
      "text": "important part of the site."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 129520.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131310.0,
      "text": "Think about what a big deal that is."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 131310.0,
      "end_time": 133870.0,
      "text": "The news feed is synonymous with Facebook."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 133870.0,
      "end_time": 137600.0,
      "text": "It's by far the biggest money making product at the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 137600.0,
      "end_time": 139960.0,
      "text": "If we're no longer looking at the news feed every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 139960.0,
      "end_time": 141950.0,
      "text": "Facebook is a much different business"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 141950.0,
      "end_time": 143339.0,
      "text": "than it ever has been before."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 143340.0,
      "end_time": 145620.0,
      "text": "Today, Facebook makes it's money by effectively"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 145620.0,
      "end_time": 148300.0,
      "text": "renting it's users attention to advertisers."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 148300.0,
      "end_time": 149610.0,
      "text": "In an encrypted messaging app,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 149610.0,
      "end_time": 151930.0,
      "text": "an advertiser can't see who you are"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 151930.0,
      "end_time": 153600.0,
      "text": "or what you might be interested in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 153600.0,
      "end_time": 155440.0,
      "text": "nearly as well as they used to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 155440.0,
      "end_time": 157880.0,
      "text": "Instead, Facebook wants to give businesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 157880.0,
      "end_time": 160130.0,
      "text": "an opportunity to let us buy and sell things"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 160130.0,
      "end_time": 162540.0,
      "text": "from within a Messenger or a WhatsApp."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 162540.0,
      "end_time": 164329.0,
      "text": "There's still a lot of details that need to be worked out."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 164330.0,
      "end_time": 166979.0,
      "text": "So, in a world where apps are encrypted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 166979.0,
      "end_time": 170350.0,
      "text": "not only can advertisers not see into your messages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 170350.0,
      "end_time": 171810.0,
      "text": "governments can't as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 171810.0,
      "end_time": 175160.0,
      "text": "If governments can't access the content of user's messages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 175160.0,
      "end_time": 177100.0,
      "text": "they're going to have a lot to say about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 177100.0,
      "end_time": 180210.0,
      "text": "We've already seen countries like Vietnam and Russia"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 180210.0,
      "end_time": 182700.0,
      "text": "pass laws requiring companies like Facebook"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 182700.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "to store any data that Facebook is collecting"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 187239.0,
      "text": "about their citizens locally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 187240.0,
      "end_time": 190600.0,
      "text": "presumably so that they can more easily access that data."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 190600.0,
      "end_time": 192220.0,
      "text": "Facebook is now saying hey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 192220.0,
      "end_time": 193630.0,
      "text": "our apps are gonna be encrypted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 193630.0,
      "end_time": 196570.0,
      "text": "there's just not gonna be a lot for you to look into."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 196570.0,
      "end_time": 198810.0,
      "text": "And Zuckerberg speculates that Facebook is actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 198810.0,
      "end_time": 201110.0,
      "text": "going to be banned in these countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 201110.0,
      "end_time": 202430.0,
      "text": "And then there's China."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 202430.0,
      "end_time": 204950.0,
      "text": "One of Mark Zuckerberg's biggest dreams over the years"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 204950.0,
      "end_time": 207119.0,
      "text": "is that Facebook would become one of the few"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 207120.0,
      "end_time": 210850.0,
      "text": "American companies to really be able to thrive in China."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 210850.0,
      "end_time": 212570.0,
      "text": "But now that the company is going to"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 212570.0,
      "end_time": 216120.0,
      "text": "enable encrypted messaging, that seems impossible."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 216120.0,
      "end_time": 218610.0,
      "text": "So encryption has benefits."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 218610.0,
      "end_time": 220190.0,
      "text": "Advertisers can't target you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 220190.0,
      "end_time": 222120.0,
      "text": "governments can't read what you're saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 222120.0,
      "end_time": 224590.0,
      "text": "there are some real drawbacks to conversation"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 224590.0,
      "end_time": 227900.0,
      "text": "moving from the town square to the living room."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 227900.0,
      "end_time": 229300.0,
      "text": "It's going to be harder to know what people"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 229300.0,
      "end_time": 232370.0,
      "text": "are saying about the politics inside their own country."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 232370.0,
      "end_time": 234840.0,
      "text": "We've already seen this in Brazil and India,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 234840.0,
      "end_time": 237240.0,
      "text": "two countries where WhatsApp is very popular."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 237240.0,
      "end_time": 239820.0,
      "text": "Misinformation has spread rapidly there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 239820.0,
      "end_time": 242200.0,
      "text": "inside these closed groups and researchers"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 242200.0,
      "end_time": 244570.0,
      "text": "have had a hard time keeping track of exactly"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 244570.0,
      "end_time": 245500.0,
      "text": "what's being said."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 245500.0,
      "end_time": 247780.0,
      "text": "So one result of this encryption might be"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 247780.0,
      "end_time": 251230.0,
      "text": "less visibility into the public discussion."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 251230.0,
      "end_time": 252959.0,
      "text": "It's trade-offs, all the way down."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 252960.0,
      "end_time": 256509.0,
      "text": "This all may come to nothing, but if it really happens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 256509.0,
      "end_time": 260690.0,
      "text": "all of a sudden, Facebook is a very different company."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 260690.0,
      "end_time": 263560.0,
      "text": "When I say Facebook, you probably think news feed."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 263560.0,
      "end_time": 265230.0,
      "text": "In the future when I say Facebook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 265230.0,
      "end_time": 267600.0,
      "text": "you might think a group text,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 267600.0,
      "end_time": 269680.0,
      "text": "you might think a small group that you're in"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 269680.0,
      "end_time": 272150.0,
      "text": "and you might never visit the news feed at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 272150.0,
      "end_time": 274469.0,
      "text": "So how do we feel about the newer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 274470.0,
      "end_time": 276820.0,
      "text": "more privacy friendly Facebook?"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 276820.0,
      "end_time": 279240.0,
      "text": "Well, privacy has a lot of benefits."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 279240.0,
      "end_time": 281550.0,
      "text": "There are many of us out there who just wanna talk"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 281550.0,
      "end_time": 284280.0,
      "text": "with our friends and our family and our co-workers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 284280.0,
      "end_time": 286479.0,
      "text": "without worrying that whatever we're saying"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 286480.0,
      "end_time": 288180.0,
      "text": "is going to come back to haunt us."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 288180.0,
      "end_time": 292120.0,
      "text": "The fact that Facebook is enabling a new way of doing that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 292120.0,
      "end_time": 293310.0,
      "text": "is pretty exciting."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 293310.0,
      "end_time": 295720.0,
      "text": "At the same time, Mark Zuckerberg has a history"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 295720.0,
      "end_time": 298470.0,
      "text": "of making grand pronouncements that never come true."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 298470.0,
      "end_time": 300290.0,
      "text": "Four years ago, he told us the news feed"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 300290.0,
      "end_time": 301800.0,
      "text": "was gonna transform into video."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 301800.0,
      "end_time": 303720.0,
      "text": "Two years ago, he published a manifesto"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 303720.0,
      "end_time": 306640.0,
      "text": "saying Facebook was going to build social infrastructure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 306640.0,
      "end_time": 308919.0,
      "text": "whatever that means, and whether this new,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 308920.0,
      "end_time": 312400.0,
      "text": "private Facebook comes into being against some"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 312400.0,
      "end_time": 315650.0,
      "text": "very long odds, is still anyone's guess."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 315650.0,
